## Get prices by Chemspace ID
At this endpoint you can find information about prices, amounts, and shipping time by a Chemspace ID. Information from all the suppliers is included.
### Example
Get prices by Chemspace ID ***CSC000000066***
### Example request:
    curl -X GET \
      "https://api.chem-space.com/v2/cs-id/CSC000000066/prices" \
      -H  "Accept: application/json; version=2.6" \
      -H  "Authorization: Bearer rVZEV12feW1axECAqJUu1dy7j8gxyNVqzSZoGY1LdKI8xvVXybBaaa7QLIJzoqfP"
